title: 3. Aha! Gaze Upon Our Heroes, As They Enter The Perilous Jungle! Oh, What A Sight To Behold, See Them Rush Through The Native Ancestry's Traps As If They Were Made Of Plastic! See Them Valiantly Kill Many A Violent Pack Animal, Who Was Merely Trying To Feed Their Family With Fresh Meat! Aha! Here Is The Exit! The First Text Has Been Completed!
